w.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-wants-china-join-global-peace-summit-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年的预期：美联储转向、通胀降温、增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/what-expect-2024-fed-pivot-cooling-inflation-easing-growth-2024-01-15/</link><description>大型银行表示，今年全球经济增长可能会放缓，但美联储立场的鸽派倾斜提高了人们对美国经济的希望，并提亮了风险资产的前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 16:07:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/what-expect-2024-fed-pivot-cooling-inflation-easing-growth-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年达沃斯：Bajaj Finserv 首席执行官表示，印度正处于 FDI 洪流的风口浪尖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-cusp-fdi-flood-bajaj-finserv-chair-says-davos-2024-01-15/</link><description>作者：A Galani 和 Anthony Slodkowski</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-cusp-fdi-flood-bajaj-finserv-chair-says-davos-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>格鲁吉亚执政党领导人访华推动深化双边关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/georgias-ruling-party-leader-visits-china-push-deeper-ties-2024-01-15/</link><description>据格鲁吉亚媒体报道，格鲁吉亚执政党领导人周一开始对中国进行为期六天的访问，这个欧盟候选成员国寻求深化与北京的关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/georgias-ruling-party-leader-visits-china-push-deeper-ties-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>玩具制造商从中国转移并非易事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/toy-manufacturers-shift-china-is-no-childs-play-2024-01-15/</link><description>面临中国成本飙升的玩具制造商在将生产转移到更便宜的地方时没有找到简单的选择。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 13:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/toy-manufacturers-shift-china-is-no-childs-play-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国与瑞士签署扩大贸易宣言</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-switzerland-sign-declaration-with-view-expanding-trade-2024-01-15/</link><description>瑞士政府表示，李强总理会见瑞士总统后，中国和瑞士周一签署了一份联合声明，同意深化合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 13:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-switzerland-sign-declaration-with-view-expanding-trade-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>危地马拉自由派新领导人反腐面临巨大障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/reformist-arevalo-assumes-guatemalan-presidency-after-opposition-delays-2024-01-15/</link><description>危地马拉新任自由派总统贝尔纳多·阿雷瓦洛(Bernardo Arevalo)在长期拖延后于周一早些时候上任，这突显了他在满足高期望和在反对派控制的国会中制定全面反腐败议程方面面临着艰巨的斗争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/reformist-arevalo-assumes-guatemalan-presidency-after-opposition-delays-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：胡塞武装袭击暴露了中国在红海的商业利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-expose-chinas-commercial-stakes-red-sea-2024-01-15/</link><description>中国呼吁停止对红海民用船只的袭击，这种袭击极大地扩大了哈马斯与以色列的冲突，并使北京在苏伊士运河沿岸的商业利益面临风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-expose-chinas-commercial-stakes-red-sea-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜黑客与犯罪分子在东南亚共享洗钱网络 - 联合国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-hackers-criminals-share-money-laundering-networks-southeast-asia-un-2024-01-15/</link><description>根据周一发布的联合国报告，朝鲜黑客正在与东南亚的欺诈者和毒贩共享洗钱和地下银行网络，赌场和加密货币交易所成为有组织犯罪的主要场所。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-hackers-criminals-share-money-laundering-networks-southeast-asia-un-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：为什么马尔代夫希望印度军队撤离</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-maldives-wants-indian-troops-out-2024-01-15/</link><description>马尔代夫新任总统于 3 月 15 日星期日为其邻国印度设定了从这个印度洋群岛小国撤军的最后期限。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-maldives-wants-indian-troops-out-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国经济增速预计将放缓至4.6%，引发政策制定者的关注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-growth-seen-slowing-46-2024-raising-heat-policymakers-2024-01-15/</link><description>路透调查显示，中国经济增长可能在2024年放缓至4.6%，并在2025年进一步降温至4.5%，在通货紧缩压力和房地产严重下滑的情况下，政策制定者推出更多刺激措施的压力加大。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-growth-seen-slowing-46-2024-raising-heat-policymakers-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>随着竞争加剧，苹果在中国以罕见的折扣出售 iPhone 15</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-15-rare-discount-china-competition-intensifies-2024-01-15/</link><description>由于全球最大智能手机市场的竞争压力日益加大，苹果公司在中国为其 iPhone 提供罕见的折扣，零售价降低了 500 元人民币（合 70 美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:58:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-15-rare-discount-china-competition-intensifies-2024-01-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>